{"tid":491350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌 私煙BB下年結婚","createTime":"2017-12-06T12:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T17:11:52.000Z","uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"43527f7c4ab42ac3b023526c3a9d92280bbfad06","tid":491350,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/06/202056_07789cd2833927fe10aab9da699888fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F06%2F202056_07789cd2833927fe10aab9da699888fd.jpg&h=f5f4c6eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171204/20233837\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171204%2F20233837&d=UZhO%2BqJXOpLBLF1A1KKHvG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a4b154f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171204%2F20233837&h=f57862c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171204/20233837</a><br />\n<br />\n上星期全城唔少港男，為咗一宗婚訊，笑中有淚，唔通可恨當中嘅新郎，唔係佢？邊位女士咁巴閉，婚事震驚全城呢？之咪就係正義聯盟主席李偲嫣。<br />\n<br />\n偲嫣喺fb晒戒，大放閃光彈。久未露面嘅李偲嫣，上星期喺佢fb公佈喜事，話會喺明年初夏結婚，同時多謝外界嘅祝福。有圖有真相？所以佢展示咗一幅婚戒照片，但就唔見人樣。據了解，李偲嫣嘅未婚夫係香港專業進修學校國際教育部副總監謝鋮浚，兩人年齡相若，同樣都係再婚，謝鋮浚早前向李偲嫣求婚並獲對方應允。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勇士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20160205/large/1454652286_674a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20160205%2Flarge%2F1454652286_674a.jpg&h=134609ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31b85d1938e1fb5143b4f93145322e974c0ba387","tid":491350,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:22:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f17bad08e2da67fea56b503f7a368a92baacada","tid":491350,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:23:22.000Z","msg":"Old news is so"},{"pid":"2aafeff01b893526fb639fd799af006f5dac5e75","tid":491350,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:24:34.000Z","msg":"心碎了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc107d2bf6b9c81731239aba496ed1a08e55376c","tid":491350,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:56:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7bb97f8fe4e836bff5f8127d017fde80a96b133","tid":491350,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:57:54.000Z","msg":"我成日都話女權主意係由港男做成<br />\n咩女港男都岩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72b68c41b31828cd1ee4f9f0318424ef4eb4db6","tid":491350,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T17:11:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}